name: Spookiez Poltergeists "The Boogeyman"
description:
Poltergeists
Special Halloween Spookiez based on real life hauntings.
 
The Boogeyman  is a mythical creature used by adults to frighten children into good behavior. The Boogeyman may target a specific act or general misbehaviour, depending on what purpose needs serving, often based on a warning from the child's authority figure. The Boogeyman is vicious and is said to steal the children at night, and even eat them. (Wikipedia)
